snippet.title: SEGA Mega Drive - PENSE BEM (Undumped Tectoy's Official Game From 2003)
snippet.description:
SEGA Genesis Pense Bem, a game by Devworks included in Tec Toy's "Super Mega Drive 3 43 Jogos" from 2003.

This is an undumped official game from 2003 made by Devworks for the Tectoy's "Super Mega Drive 3 43 Jogos" from 2003.

There's a dump of an inferior version from 2004 with PSG musics instead of sampled songs.

FUN FACT: The "Super Mega Drive 3 43 Jogos" (Tectoy's Mega Drive III PCI MD III REV 10.0) was the last Tectoy's Mega Drive with the ASIC 315-6123 before the GOAC "TECTOY".
